{"tid":547064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"周庭被DQ, 美國駐港領事及英國外交部發聲","createTime":"2018-02-01T05:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T09:32:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"495e985be8788e023d6cd899bc189cd73524acce","tid":547064,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180201/57779344?_ga=2.67649299.385281381.1517192222-509722967.1481259919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F57779344%3F_ga%3D2.67649299.385281381.1517192222-509722967.1481259919&d=tKULNKj27C%2FG92dllZ2ZRDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e6fc8adc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F57779344%3F_ga%3D2.67649299.385281381.1517192222-509722967.1481259919&h=15ee87a1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180201/57779344?_ga=2.67649299.385281381.1517192222-509722967.1481259919</a><br />\n<br />\n【立會補選】周庭被DQ 英國外交部及美駐港領館發聲<br />\n<br />\n11,285<br />\n最後更新: 0201 13:38 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0201 11:29<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志周庭被政府剝奪參選立法會資格，歐盟日前發表聲明，表示此舉會損害香港聲譽。本報向美國駐港總領事館查詢對此事看法，發言人指，他們早前已表明，美國堅定支持香港的高度自治、法治、對人權和基本自由尊重：「我們支持表達自由，並相信當不同政見可以獲表達時，才是對社會最好。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，繼歐盟之後，英國外交部也發聲明表示憂慮。英國外交部發言人指，被選舉權是港人的基本權利，受《基本法》第26條及《香港人權法案條例》保障。而高度自治、權利和自由是香港生活模式的核心，應受到充分尊重。<br />\n<br />\n【美領館回應全文】<br />\n&ldquo;As we have said before, the United States firmly supports Hong Kong's high degree of autonomy, rule of law, and respect for human rights and fundamental freedoms. We support freedom of expression and believe that societies are best served when diverse political views can be expressed.&rdquo;<br />\n【英國外交部回應全文】<br />\n&ldquo;We are concerned by the rejection of Agnes Chow&rsquo;s nomination for the forthcoming Legislative Council by-election. The right to stand for election is a fundamental right enshrined in Article 26 of the Basic Law of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region and the Hong Kong Bill of Rights.<br />\nHong Kong&rsquo;s high degree of autonomy, and its rights and freedoms, are central to its way of life, and it is important that they should be fully respected.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"0cfc8e2c7bef21d9da0d21c5d121b4745cddcfae","tid":547064,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25af857f0f8fac632c41e319bb723100ddaab8b","tid":547064,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":34,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:52:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01e1018811d00bf41a810aff2d5921394651c77b","tid":547064,"uid":45749,"like":30,"dislike":3,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"啲鬼佬咪又係得把口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw樓上條仆街冚家陷五毛死全家"},{"pid":"e8f51af4726f9fc4d3f140cca1e2194f8ed36327","tid":547064,"uid":63669,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"最好再瘋狂DQ甚至隨意捉人座監 , 令美國早日取消關係法"},{"pid":"174a1009338a3a6c080ce5a6a71c84f31b691a49","tid":547064,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:04:51.000Z","msg":"華春袋:強烈反對干涉中國內政"},{"pid":"2646aaa8f015b8eaf3a099886a2e7c0ba02f7098","tid":547064,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:15:07.000Z","msg":"噏完要做嘢先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684b31249bc051cf217d7a03f44f2ae0d576f65e","tid":547064,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"英美仲想靠香港金融搵錢<br />\n所以永遠都係得把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f75b79b6550f353401f1b5fa617897201b6980f","tid":547064,"uid":21017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"174a1009338a3a6c080ce5a6a71c84f31b691a4